data.revised_prompt: Generate a sophisticated, high-quality image of a 'Whiskey Ginger Twist' cocktail placed under soft, warm lighting. This delightful concoction is served in a crystal-clear, short rocks glass which showcases the drink's warm amber hue. A subtle effervescence can be observed, courtesy of the ginger ale in the drink, which adds a playful contrast. To add a dash of color, a vibrant green lime wheel is perched upon the rim of the glass. A deep mahogany wood texture forms the backdrop, enhancing the rich tones of the cocktail and making the composition appealing and inviting. Ensure the image has a clear background with soft focus and no text or watermarks, so as to capture the finesse and accuracy of a professional food photographer's shot.
